---
title: Autumnal Baked Pork and Apple Meatballs with Onion Gravy, Mash and Cabbage
description: Designed by our chefs for a balanced lifestyle, these Autumnal Baked Pork and Apple Meatballs hit the spot. Pairing apples, a rich onion gravy and seasonal cabbage makes a comforting meal that's perfect for autumn.
